00:40:33.850 --> 00:40:35.610
all the points.

00:40:35.610 --> 00:40:40.330
So obviously, cosines
and sines, so we're

00:40:40.330 --> 00:40:44.050
going to get results
between 1 and -1.

00:40:44.050 --> 00:40:44.550
Let's see.

