on this number line

00:41:33.110 --> 00:41:38.740
into this brave new dimension
by using their cosine times

00:41:38.740 --> 00:41:39.830
Pi over 4.

00:41:39.830 --> 00:41:42.660
So all right, great.

00:41:42.660 --> 00:41:46.920
So let's do the pluses first.

00:41:46.920 --> 00:41:51.110
